{
  "stem": "11184.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 16.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and we weren't treated badly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It wasn't-- it wasn't too bad over there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were given nice meals, nice.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What happened?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They wanted us strong to send out to work, so they didn't want weak and sick people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Were you feeling-- could you eat there?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then-- then.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My appetite came back, and I could eat, yeah.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Mhm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I got back to myself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and then-- and then we stayed there till they started to build barracks for all the other Auschwitz people, when-- when-- when Bergen-Belsen became hell.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we left, you know, I mean, every few weeks another group-- how they remembered, because their-- their organization is so great, the Germans.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They knew exactly who came to be sent out, because so many people arrived there, you know?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I-- we were the last group to go, me and my mother and a few other people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Out of Auschwitz into--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Out of Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Out of Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Let's see.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "August, September, October-- October, or half of November or the end of October.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We just did nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As I said, it-- it was-- but we were told then that they want us to be strong because they need us for work.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But by the time people were coming in from Auschwitz, other people, but this was not the selected group anymore.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The other people stayed over there till they all died and Bergen-Belsen was a horrible place, horrible.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, so many people died out and from sicknesses and diseases.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- but we were the lucky ones to get out, me and my mother and a few others.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On a-- on a-- on a train.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On the train.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were going and going.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
